{"title":"赠缅甸友人","authors":["陈毅"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":12,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"赠缅甸友人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈毅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我住江之头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你住江之尾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彼此情无限，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共饮一江水。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我吸川上流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你喝川下水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"川流去不息，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彼此共甘美。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彼此为近邻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"友谊长积累，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不老如青山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不断似流水。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彼此地相联，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依山复靠水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反帝获自由，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和平同一轨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彼此是亲戚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"语言多同轨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"团结而互助，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和平力量伟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"临水叹浩淼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"登山歌石磊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山山似北向，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"条条南流水。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1957年12月14日"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}